  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kinkoi: Golden Time is a Japanese-style visual novel produced by Saga Planets, a Japanese developer of romance VNs. <br>It is the official extra story to Kinkoi: Golden Loveriche.<br>The game won numerous awards in the year of its release in Japan for its art, music, characters, and story.</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/806da525724400fba6e051a36e1464c0.poster.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/806da525724400fba6e051a36e1464c0.webm?t=1670679627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/806da525724400fba6e051a36e1464c0.mp4?t=1670679627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to Noble Private Academy, an institution that cultivates the wealthiest, most well-connected students in all of Japan! At this boarding school, one must be willing to accept all of its refined and dignified teachings or be met with strict opposition! <br><br>The hero of our story, Ichimatsu Ouro, transferred to this very academy three months prior through extenuating circumstances and he's now faced with a brand-new challenge: the holiday season! With New Year's right around the corner, he yearns to reach his peak, golden self.<br><br>Will that diverse golden shade live on forever?!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/479140c4acfd78c3dfbf79121a341866.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=920 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/58bc645d1d401fdde2df37f504e69e7c.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=957 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/7a34a7e293a080206ab1dbbf449d7564.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=815 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/19dca66086e1920b7180b8b80ee9b4e1.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=802 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/5f7f6ff5e19cb6881702fcfa53c17a3f.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=775 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/5241b08d4a1ec1c8fd15990b5820d258.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=950 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/624eec356e9b8fc9edb42f2d7ceff02d.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=751 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/e931fa50d25bd55e1f09aab033436646.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=656 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kinkoi: Golden Time is a Japanese-style visual novel produced by Saga Planets, a Japanese developer of romance VNs. <br>It is the official extra story to Kinkoi: Golden Loveriche.<br>The game won numerous awards in the year of its release in Japan for its art, music, characters, and story.</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/806da525724400fba6e051a36e1464c0.poster.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/806da525724400fba6e051a36e1464c0.webm?t=1670679627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/806da525724400fba6e051a36e1464c0.mp4?t=1670679627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to Noble Private Academy, an institution that cultivates the wealthiest, most well-connected students in all of Japan! At this boarding school, one must be willing to accept all of its refined and dignified teachings or be met with strict opposition! <br><br>The hero of our story, Ichimatsu Ouro, transferred to this very academy three months prior through extenuating circumstances and he's now faced with a brand-new challenge: the holiday season! With New Year's right around the corner, he yearns to reach his peak, golden self.<br><br>Will that diverse golden shade live on forever?!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/479140c4acfd78c3dfbf79121a341866.avif?t=1670679627\" width=600 height=920 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985260/extras/58bc645d1d401fdde2df37f504e